videos.description: Georgia Tech QB TaQuon Marshall avoids being sacked and runs for a 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Marshall scrambles for Georgia Tech TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech coach Paul Johnson is happy with the team's defense, but says the team's offense needs to improve in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Johnson happy with Yellow Jackets’ defense in first half) 2017/9/30

videos.headline: Johnson happy with Yellow Jackets' defense in first half

videos.description: UNC's Cole Holcomb recovers the fumble when the Tar Heels need it most.

videos.headline: North Carolina forces key turnover

videos.description: KirVonte Benson finds space and takes off down the sideline for a long touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech breaks off 63-yard TD run to extend lead

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall finds Ricky Jeune in the end zone to give Georgia Tech a 24-0 lead over North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jeune makes diving TD catch to extend Yellow Jackets' lead) 2017/09/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jeune makes diving TD catch to extend Yellow Jackets' lead

videos.description: Jordon Brown makes his way into the end zone from 8 yards out for North Carolina's first score of the day.

videos.headline: UNC gets on the board with 8-yard rushing TD

videos.description: Matthew Jordan runs through a defender and scores for a 5-yard touchdown, giving the Yellow Jackets a 33-7 lead over the Tar Heels.

videos.headline: Jordan's late TD seals Georgia Tech victory
